	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我可是為<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />好才給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />建議，<delay frames="40" />
