一想到有這種可能性，<delay20 /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就覺得好難堪，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不用太在意啦</message>
	<message label="103_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣啊</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽你這麼說，<delay20 />
